{"tid":1888390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會工場生產首批口罩　檢測合格後可正式投產","createTime":"2020-02-20T07:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T07:37:51.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2856d6c1b93c04eea8e0352a95704497ad229905","tid":1888390,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"工聯會工場生產首批口罩 檢測合格後可正式投產<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1509662_2_L_20200220130852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1509662_2_L_20200220130852.jpg&h=ace65961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工聯會開設口罩工場，已完成生產首批口罩，預料需要兩星期檢測。（楊毓昇攝）<br />\n<br />\n工聯會開設口罩工場，製造了數十個口罩以作檢測，預料需時約兩星期，如果成功，便可正式生產，首批將免費派給長者、長期病患者及清潔保安服務業人員等。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會表示，由構思到生產需時3星期，首條半自動生產線每個月可生產10萬個口罩，第二條生產線會是全自動生產線，期間需要搶購原材料、找無塵空間、從內地運送相關機器等，亦有向懲教署取經，政府科技部門有提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會希望口罩工場的生產的口罩有助應急，支援前線工友。"},{"pid":"5658e9df849fa72b0b9251ff94bf2cb99fc9f5f2","tid":1888390,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:27:34.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾陸期牆紙】 Failed State<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1886293/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1886293/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OffS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=9a6a1eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OffS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=5e181d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F